Title: The Patience of Princes
Description:
The centaur's report of Primalist forces pushing into the underground after Fyrakk changes the situation. Wrathion and I believe it would be a tactical mistake to dawdle here any longer, waiting for Ebyssian and his devotee to arrive.

We still wish for you to join us. If you are ready, then we three should proceed together.
ObjectivesText: Delve underground and fell the Primalist blockade.
